summary: SummaryShines like glass. Feels like air. That high-shine look is so low maintenance with this non-sticky, hydrating and addictive MAC Lipglass Air Lipgloss that delivers light-as-air wear and next-level nourishing care.
details: DetailsBenefitsNon-sticky, glass-like shineLightweight, comfortable formulaHydrates lips instantly and all day, 8 hoursLips appear smoother by visibly reducing the appearance of lip linesProvides plumper, fuller-looking lipsKey IngredientsNourishes lips with a 7% blend of pure botanical oils, including coconut, jojoba and meadowfoam seedFormulated WithoutAnimal-derived ingredientsItem 2635742How To UseEvenly coat lips using the soft, paddle-shaped applicator.Pro tip: Pair with a Lip Pencil and define before you shine for instantly fuller-looking lips.Line after you shine for a more natural-looking effect.IngredientsHydrogenated Polyisobutene, Octyldodecanol, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Ethylene/Propylene/Styrene Copolymer, Silica, Tocopheryl Acetate, Limnanthes Alba (Meadowfoam) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Tetrahexyldecyl Ascorbate, Vanillin, Accharin, Polydecene, Butylene/Ethylene/Styrene Copolymer, Hydrogenated Lecithin, Pentaerythrityl Tetradi-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Caprylyl Glycol, Hexylene Glycol, Bht, Phenoxyethanol, [+/-Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491), Iron Oxides (CI 77492), Iron Oxides (CI 77499), Red 6 (CI 15850), Red 7 (CI 15850), Red 28 (CI 45410), Red 30 (CI 73360), Red 33 (CI 17200), Yellow 5 (CI 19140), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Red 6 Lake (CI 15850), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Red 28 Lake (CI 45410), Red 30 Lake (CI 73360), Red 33 Lake (CI 17200), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140), Yellow 6 Lake (CI 15985)].Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Evenly coat lips using the soft, paddle-shaped applicator.Pro tip: Pair with a Lip Pencil and define before you shine for instantly fuller-looking lips.Line after you shine for a more natural-looking effect.

reviews.headline: Horrible
reviews.comments: This lip gloss completely ruined my lips and gave me a bad reaction which is CRAZY cuz nothing does that to me. I thought maybe I was the bottle wrong and it was a plumping gloss because after two days of wearing it, day 3 I woke up with my lips swollen….

reviews.headline: this one is special
reviews.comments: I have alot of lip gloss, a whole drawer full of high end and luxury brand glosses. From Chanel to Rituel refilled, to Bobbi Brown, the list could go on for the rest of the day. So while I was excited when I first saw these, since Im not a fan of the other MAC gloss, I wasn't really expecting exceptional... Boy was I wrong!!! I only ordered one, which was hard because the shade selection is amazing,  but I got 225 Instinct. This stuff is perfection. Its addictive. Its smells like a powdery vanilla, with a hint of baby doll hair. it doesnt really have a taste but Im obsessed with the scent. Color is perfect,  and still noticeable even though I have a dark tan right now. Its stays in place, isn't at all sticky but not too slick, just right honestly, reminds me of the Laura Mercier texture, or those Bobbi Brown oil glosses (which are the perfect texture in my opinion). the tube is pretty and sturdy, has a firm click at the end when you shut it, and the doe foot is straight and flat but fluffy. EASYYYY to apply.i love everything about it and carry it in my purse. It went straight to the top spot honestly... I need to get more shades. its literally 10/10!!!

reviews.headline: so pretty
reviews.comments: I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes. The shade is so pretty and not sticky at all. The shimmer is not overpowering or chunky which is great. I can really see myself wearing this in the fall either alone or on top of other lipsticks. Truly is a good formula.

reviews.headline: My go to lipgloss
reviews.comments: I'm absolutely loving the new MAC Lipgloss! I received this stunning product in the shade "Frozen" for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes. The lipgloss has a gorgeous, glass-like finish that makes my lips look beautiful and hydrated, all without that heavy, sticky feeling that some glosses have. I carry it with me everywhere and apply it whenever I want to freshen up my look. I've already received several compliments on it! I will definitely be purchasing more in the future. My only minor complaint is that I wish it lasted a bit longer.

reviews.headline: I loved it!
reviews.comments:
This MAC gloss exceeded my expectations. The shine is beautiful and the color is super flattering. The best thing is that it is not sticky at all, it feels light on the lips and comfortable all day.

I love how it leaves the lips with a juicy effect and with a shine that does not look exaggerated. In addition, the packaging is elegant and the applicator distributes the product very well.

reviews.headline: i love this
reviews.comments: I absolutely loved my experience with MAC Lipglass Air Non-Sticky Gloss in SUBLIME! I applied it both during the day and evening and found it to be versatile and long-lasting. The gloss glided on smoothly, and I appreciated its non-sticky texture, which felt comfortable throughout wear. The subtle scent was pleasant and not overwhelming, adding to the overall luxurious feel of the product. I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes.

reviews.headline: Best lipgloss ever!
reviews.comments:
Best lipgloss ever!
I don't usually get high end lip gloss, and let me tell ya! It is worth it to spend more. This is hands down the best lipgloss I have ever tried. I carry it with me everywhere and it is perfect for every occasion. I wasn't head over heels for the price, but I do want one in every shade. Not sticky at all and definitely feels hydrating. Absolutely would recommend to anyone. I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes.

reviews.headline: Love this lip gloss!
reviews.comments: Okay first off, this stuff smells like a dreamy cupcake. It is so shimmery/sparkly. The lip brush is so soft. It truly feels like glass when it's drying. My lips are so soft! I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes.

reviews.comments: I loved this gloss! it has such a nice finish and leaves your lips feeling moisturized. it smells great and is not sticky. has a great scent.  I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes.

reviews.comments: I absolutely love this lip gloss! Smooth, glassy finish, non sticky and perfect for everyday wear. I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes.

faceoff_positive.comments: I was out pounding brewski's with my broski's. I was heading home when my chopper( motorcycle) broke down on the wrong side of town. I was alone on the streets.  All I had was a set of brass knuckles a switch blade and some lip gloss i had just picked up from my Mac Makeup Artist earlier that day. My cell phone was dead and I had no money.  Great. In the distance I heard some noise. I saw 4 dark shadows.  I grabbed my knuckles and got my blade ready. I had glossed my lips up before I left the bar to protect my lips from the elements as I rode home. As I stood there ready to defend myself and my property in the dark night my lips looked glossy and shiny with a nice soft pink glow. 4 hoodlums emerged from the dark. They were all bigger then me. I knew I was in for a fight. I flashed my blade and showed them my knuckles. U ready to dance I asked?? Hey they said. Ur lips.  We just want to know wut u got on. I put away my knuckles and my blade and pulled out my gloss. I said it was Mac Lipglass AirNon StickyGloss. The stuff goes on silky smooth keeping my lips hydrated and healthy with a nice pink shine. I told them who my makeup artist was and gave them her phone number.  They said they would help me with my chopper and give me a ride home. They said next time I come to town to give them a call we'll go get brewski's and pizza.  Cool . I just made some new friends.  Now go get some gloss and tell me ur story!!
faceoff_positive.headline: Dark Streets And Glossy Pink Lips

faceoff_negative.comments:
I received this product for free from Topbox Marketing for testing and review purposes. I wanted to start off by saying that I'm a huge fan of the brand and the ORIGINAL Lipglass, along with the Cremesheen version that I really wish they would expand on. I have a limited edition Cremesheen glass that I adore(Krazy Kahuna) and I have not found anything close to the pigment and longevity of that absolute gem of a lipgloss. 

This new revision of Lipglass I'm assuming is for all the people that claim the original is too sticky. Newsflash: lipgloss MUST be somewhat sticky if you want any kind of staying power and for it to not just slide off your lips. This air version does feel incredibly nourishing, but it does not have the thickness that the original has and therefore does not have its longevity. 

Also, where is the pigment?! 😭 I know that it claims to be "sheer" but sheer does not mean completely translucent and clear! As my first picture shows, the lip gloss has absolutely no pigment and my boyfriend described it as looking like chapstick. The second picture is me with a  bunch of lip liner and the Instinct Air Lipglass on top, and while it does look nice, I could have achieved that look(and an even juicier more "glass like" look) with a cheap lip gloss. I really hope they don't completely replace the original Lipglass with this thin, no-pigment, and less shine version.
faceoff_negative.headline: Dissapointing
